\par\pard\plain \sa180\sb180\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs26\b1\i0\cf7 Liz }{\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf6 (impressed by Sarah\loch\af5\hich\af5\dbch\af5\uc1\u8217\'92s beauty)}{\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 :}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93She is quite beautiful. That skirt suit was fabulous. I\u8217\'92m afraid to even ask him much that cost.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 Evan:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93I haven\u8217\'92t met him yet, but her father is a self-made millionaire. He taught Sarah everything he knows about running a successful business. Sarah doesn\u8217\'92t really care one way or another about the designer clothes that she owns.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b1\i0\cf7 Liz }{\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf6 (briefly interrupts, still impressed with Sarah)}{\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 :}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93For someone doesn\u8217\'92t care, she has great taste.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b1\i0\cf7 Evan }{\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf6 (worried he was misunderstood)}{\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 :}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93She definitely appreciates the nice clothes, and you\u8217\'92re right, she has spectacular taste. Her apartment is to die for. But the reason that everything is designer, is her father\u8217\'92s choice. She told me that he insists she buys those close because in his opinion, walking into a meeting of any kind wearing a suit that costs over thousand dollars with expensive shoes to match garner\u8217\'92s immediate respect without a word needing to be said.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 Liz:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93That is actually true. I\u8217\'92ve seen that many times at the office. A well-dressed man, or in Sarah\u8217\'92s case, woman does seem to be treated with more respect the better dressed they are. And Sarah wears that outfit well. I know sense that she was trying to show off her father\u8217\'92s wealth.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b1\i0\cf7 Evan }{\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf6 (grateful)}{\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 :}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93I\u8217\'92m glad you can see that in her. She in no way considers herself superior to anyone. Unfortunately, because she so smart, she\u8217\'92s literally a genius, sometimes I think people think she looks down upon. They don\u8217\'92t understand or like I understand her.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 Evan thought for a moment about how to say what he had to say next in the right way. Still unsure with what words to use, he just opened his mouth and share his thoughts.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b1\i0\cf7 Evan }{\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf6 (continued)}{\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 :}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93Don\u8217\'92t be upset if it takes her a while to warm up. Sarah was an only child, and her parents had a unique way of raising her. They focused almost exclusively on academics and training her to one day take over father\u8217\'92s business \endash \u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b1\i0\cf7 Liz }{\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf6 (stopped Evan in his tracks)}{\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 :}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93Evan, you have nothing to worry about. If you like her, then will like her too.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 Evan\loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8217\'92s expression changed. Liz\u8217\'92s words reminded him that he more than likes Sarah he is head over heels in love with her. He was not afraid to express his feelings.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b1\i0\cf7 Evan }{\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf6 (sincerely, passionately)}{\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 :}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93Liz, I don\u8217\'92t just like her I am in love with her.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 Liz could see how sincere and passionate Evan was saying these words.}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 Liz:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93Then we are sure to love her too.\u8221\'94}
