\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 Liz:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93How do you think she feels about you? You guys get along well?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 Evan:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93She loves me too. We get along perfectly. She not only makes you want to be a better man. She has made me a better man.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f1\fs26\b1\i0\cf7 Liz }{\f5\fs26\b0\i1\cf6 (curious)}{\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 :}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93How so?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f3\fs22\b1\i0\cf7 Evan:}{\f2\fs22\b0\i0  }{\f2\fs22\b0\i0\cf8 \loch\af2\hich\af2\dbch\af2\uc1\u8220\'93Before I met her, I didn\u8217\'92t take myself seriously. I didn\u8217\'92t take life seriously. Yes, I have fun. But I learned that I can still have fun and take myself and life seriously.\u8221\'94}
